{
  "stem": "8679.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't care if she wanted me to live, because it says, in the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Ghost, Amen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And refers to the Christian belief, but it also has a lot of the Ten Commandments in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was found in Germany in the year-- and it was found in Germany in the year 1700.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what I finally was reading.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it continuously said in order that it will protect you, you have to believe in the power of this letter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you see, before I read it, just because she told me that it will protect me if I believe in it, I believed in it without having laid eyes on it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I carried the letter with me through the death march that lasted nearly two weeks, through liberation, and my struggle to stand on my own feet.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Today, April-- January 23, 1996, I have my letter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I continue to believe in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We never knew where they take us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was all the time unknown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As to food, we got maybe twice a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the street are no kitchens-- there's no soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't get water either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At one point, I was so desperately thirsty, I must have lost my mind when I approached a guard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Austrians have a different accent, like I have a different accent speaking German than the German have.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I approached him and asked him, please, may I have a little bit of water?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To do that, I can assure you, I must have lost my mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me one look-- he was big guy-- stretched out his hand, and slapped me in the face that I can feel the sting almost.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was his answer.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
